      <description>&lt;div id="storytext" class="storytext storylocation linkLocation"&gt;       &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Good morning. You're reading the Up First newsletter. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/newsletter/news" target="_blank"&gt;Subscribe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; here to get it delivered to your inbox, and &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/podcasts/510318/up-first/" target="_blank"&gt;listen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; to the Up First podcast for all the news you need to start your day.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;Life Kit's Guide to Dry January&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If your New Year's resolution is to take a break from drinking alcohol, we've got some guidance that could help.&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Life Kit &lt;/em&gt;put together some strategies to &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2020/01/02/781673495/6-ways-to-take-a-break-from-drinking" target="_blank"&gt;help you stay sober&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;for Dry January or sober-ish if you're doing "damp" January. The team created a guide to the month as a &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/12/26/g-s1-36783/give-up-alcohol-dry-january-october-sober-curious" target="_blank"&gt;limited-run newsletter series&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-37669" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 4500;         --source-height: 3000;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4500x3000+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fad%2F44%2F7aa4d8a1489d960c3b79a1822b82%2Flk-dry-january-newsletter-harlan-11.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4500x3000+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fad%2F44%2F7aa4d8a1489d960c3b79a