lity/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F18%2F0c%2F36e84485400c934a60d1dee937a3%2Fgettyimages-1689515342.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3936x2624+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F18%2F0c%2F36e84485400c934a60d1dee937a3%2Fgettyimages-1689515342.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3936x2624+0+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F18%2F0c%2F36e84485400c934a60d1dee937a3%2Fgettyimages-1689515342.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3936x2624+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F18%2F0c%2F36e84485400c934a60d1dee937a3%2Fgettyimages-1689515342.jpg" class="img" alt="Avocados grow on trees in an orchard in the municipality of Ario de Rosales, Michoacan State, Mexico, on Sept. 21, 2023. Tariffs on Mexican imports would have a big effect on avocados in the U.S." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 Avocados grow on trees in an orchard in the municipality of Ario de Rosales, Michoacan State, Mexico, on Sept. 21, 2023. Tariffs on Mexican imports would have a big effect on avocados in the U.S.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Alfredo Estrella/AFP via Getty Images                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;President-elect Donald Trump's proposed tariffs on Mexico could impact how much you pay for avocados at the store. &lt;/strong&gt;About 90% of avocados consumed in the U.S. are imported and the majority come from Mexico. Trump said he plans to impose a 25% tariff on Mexican imports, but it's unclear if they will be implemented or if they will serve as a negotiating tactic. &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/12/23/nx-s1-5214649/avocados-tariffs-mexico-trump-organic" target="_blank"&gt;Here's what to know about avocados&lt;/a&gt;, tariffs, and why so many avocados are grown in Mexico. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;ul class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;🥑 &lt;strong&gt;The price of avocados may not go up by the full 25%&lt;/strong&gt;, but it could be pretty close, due to there being few options on where to source them, food economist David Ortega told NPR.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;🥑 &lt;strong&gt;Mexico emerged as the largest foreign supplier&lt;/strong&gt; of fruits and vegetables to the U.S. due to its proximity to the U.S.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;🥑 &lt;strong&gt;Mexico's weather allows for year-round production&lt;/strong&gt; of avocados and producers have access to cheap labor.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;🥑 &lt;strong&gt;In addition to the threat of tariffs&lt;/strong&gt;, the avocado industry is facing challenges such as climate change and the fact that avocados require large amounts of water to grow.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;3 things to know before you go&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-39769" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 5280;         --source-height: 3521;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/webp" /&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5280x3521+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Ffe%2Fa8579dde45d582b733dce8639a09%2Fap24289447391081.jpg" class="img" alt="Walmart delivery drivers were pushed to use illegally opened payments accounts, a federal lawsuit alleges." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 Walmart delivery drivers were pushed to use illegally opened payments accounts, a federal lawsuit alleges.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Nam Y. Huh/AP                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;ol class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A federal lawsuit alleges Walmart and payments platform Branch Messenger cost delivery drivers over $10 million in fees&lt;/strong&gt; by creating deposit accounts for them &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/12/23/nx-s1-5237492/cfpb-sues-walmart-over-delivery-drivers-illegal-deposit-accounts" target="_blank"&gt;without consent and requiring their use&lt;/a&gt; to get paid.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Container Store, a 46-year-old retail chain, filed for Chapter 11 bankruptcy&lt;/strong&gt; protection on Sunday. The company said this &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/12/23/nx-s1-5237406/container-store-bankruptcy-stores" target="_blank"&gt;will have no impact on customers&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are mashed potatoes on your holiday menu?&lt;/strong&gt; If so, Dan Souza of America's Test Kitchen has &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/12/24/nx-s1-5225373/this-mashed-potatoes-recipe-breaks-all-the-rules-for-a-tasty-twist-on-the-holiday-dish" target="_blank"&gt;a recipe and cooking tips&lt;/a&gt; that will have you ready to whip them up perfectly.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;       &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This newsletter was edited by &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/people/g-s1-2467/obed-manuel"target="_blank"   &gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Obed Manuel&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
