omen skateboarding in their traditional dresses and bowler hats. You can see the vibrant and telling images by &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/goats-and-soda/2024/12/20/g-s1-37751/photos-skateboarders-food-fishing-ambulances-best-of-2024" target="_blank"&gt;clicking here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;3 things to know before you go&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-39631" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 4156;         --source-height: 3325;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4156x3325+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F33%2Fd2%2F21f902c54df7a93fd2057a1b4608%2Fap24222707931218.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4156x3325+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F33%2Fd2%2F21f902c54df7a93fd2057a1b4608%2Fap24222707931218.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4156x3325+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F33%2Fd2%2F21f902c54df7a93fd2057a1b4608%2Fap24222707931218.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4156x3325+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F33%2Fd2%2F21f902c54df7a93fd2057a1b4608%2Fap24222707931218.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4156x3325+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F33%2Fd2%2F21f902c54df7a93fd2057a1b4608%2Fap24222707931218.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4156x3325+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F33%2Fd2%2F21f902c54df7